msgid ""
"Understanding the differences between local and remote tools helps you "
"choose the right approach for your needs."
msgstr "了解本地工具与远程工具之间的差异，有助于您选择适合需求的正确方法。"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:22
#: 4833de53662c41e2bb2e2b15b450645a
msgid "**Key Differences:**"
msgstr "**主要差异：**"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:24
#: 7a233937c671428c8d0d7a96d765230e
msgid "Aspect | Local Tools | Remote Tools |"
msgstr "方面 | 本地工具 | 远程工具 |"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:25
#: 4fd21060366a42fd825b9d75591d25d8
msgid ""
"|--------|-------------|--------------| | **Performance** | High (no network"
" overhead) | Lower (network latency) | | **Development** | Simple Python "
"classes | MCP servers or API wrappers | | **Deployment** | Part of "
"ToolUniverse | Independent servers | | **Scalability** | Limited by process "
"| Highly scalable | | **Integration** | Full ToolUniverse access | Limited "
"to MCP/API | | **Contribution** | Requires ``__init__.py`` changes | No code"
" changes needed |"
msgstr ""
"|--------|-------------|--------------|  \n"
"| **性能** | 高（无网络开销） | 较低（存在网络延迟） |  \n"
"| **开发** | 简单的 Python 类 | MCP 服务器或 API 封装 |  \n"
"| **部署** | ToolUniverse 的一部分 | 独立服务器 |  \n"
"| **可扩展性** | 受进程限制 | 高度可扩展 |  \n"
"| **集成** | 完全访问 ToolUniverse | 仅限 MCP/API |  \n"
"| **贡献** | 需要修改 ``__init__.py`` | 无需代码修改 |"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:33
#: 7716ede3efa24c90b3a47d50bac620b7
msgid ""
"**When to Use Local Tools:** - Data processing and analysis - File "
"manipulation utilities - Simple API wrappers - Tools that need full "
"ToolUniverse integration"
msgstr ""
"**何时使用本地工具：**  \n"
"- 数据处理与分析  \n"
"- 文件操作工具  \n"
"- 简单的 API 封装程序  \n"
"- 需要完整 ToolUniverse 集成的工具"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:39
#: c87cb586483f4561b86bd9888344779a
msgid ""
"**When to Use Remote Tools:** - External service integration - Heavy "
"computational tasks - Microservice architecture - Tools in different "
"programming languages"
msgstr ""
"**何时使用远程工具：**  \n"
"- 外部服务集成  \n"
"- 高强度计算任务  \n"
"- 微服务架构  \n"
"- 不同编程语言的工具"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:46
#: 46af4e256f3c4cbd8e985135a0caf33a
msgid "Architecture Details"
msgstr "架构详情"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:48
#: 7466e9cb8bf942f0addf283f459dea6a
msgid ""
"**ToolUniverse Core Components:** - **Tool Registry**: Manages tool "
"discovery and registration - **Execution Engine**: Handles tool execution "
"and error management - **Configuration System**: Manages tool parameters and"
" settings - **MCP Integration**: Connects with remote tools via MCP protocol"
msgstr ""
"**ToolUniverse 核心组件：**  \n"
"- **工具注册表**：管理工具的发现和注册  \n"
"- **执行引擎**：处理工具执行和错误管理  \n"
"- **配置系统**：管理工具参数和设置  \n"
"- **MCP 集成**：通过 MCP 协议连接远程工具"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:54
#: b1c5be435cd24cd3b05d1b4f7aa152ed
msgid ""
"**Tool Lifecycle:** 1. **Registration**: Tools register with the registry 2."
" **Discovery**: ToolUniverse discovers available tools 3. **Configuration**:"
" Tools load their configuration 4. **Execution**: Tools are called with "
"parameters 5. **Response**: Results are returned to the caller"
msgstr ""
"**工具生命周期：**  \n"
"1. **注册**：工具在注册表中进行注册  \n"
"2. **发现**：ToolUniverse 发现可用的工具  \n"
"3. **配置**：工具加载其配置  \n"
"4. **执行**：工具根据参数被调用  \n"
"5. **响应**：结果返回给调用方"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:61
#: 097a492c502c4b8b943e2bb7fe7cf555
msgid ""
"**Error Handling:** - Input validation at multiple levels - Graceful error "
"recovery - Comprehensive error reporting - Timeout management for remote "
"tools"
msgstr ""
"**错误处理：**  \n"
"- 多层次的输入验证  \n"
"- 优雅的错误恢复  \n"
"- 全面的错误报告  \n"
"- 远程工具的超时管理"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:68
#: ba7bb6cbaa6b4d33b2bc0f59f1661c50
msgid "Best Practices"
msgstr "最佳实践"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:70
#: bb81100409a341efb0f392564fe9f236
msgid ""
"**Local Tools:** - Keep tools focused and single-purpose - Use proper error "
"handling - Implement input validation - Add comprehensive tests - Document "
"all parameters clearly"
msgstr ""
"**本地工具：**  \n"
"- 保持工具专注且单一用途  \n"
"- 使用适当的错误处理  \n"
"- 实现输入验证  \n"
"- 添加全面的测试  \n"
"- 清晰地记录所有参数"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:77
#: 4b93c9a407574406a8119e89132e8b07
msgid ""
"**Remote Tools:** - Implement proper authentication - Use circuit breakers "
"for resilience - Add retry logic for transient failures - Monitor "
"performance and errors - Provide clear deployment documentation"
msgstr ""
"**远程工具：**  \n"
"- 实施适当的身份验证  \n"
"- 使用断路器提高系统弹性  \n"
"- 为瞬态故障添加重试逻辑  \n"
"- 监控性能和错误  \n"
"- 提供清晰的部署文档"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:84
#: 7bc1a51450ae4fd3abb17a0a8634cf38
msgid ""
"**General:** - Follow naming conventions - Use descriptive parameter names -"
" Provide clear error messages - Include usage examples - Test with real-"
"world data"
msgstr ""
"**通用规则：**  \n"
"- 遵循命名规范  \n"
"- 使用具有描述性的参数名称  \n"
"- 提供清晰的错误信息  \n"
"- 包括使用示例  \n"
"- 使用真实数据进行测试"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:92
#: 76baaa4fc651425785794080cf5ede7d
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "故障排除"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:94
#: 9eab5eb8cb634ce0b1d241900f1d7e9f
msgid "**Common Issues:**"
msgstr "**常见问题：**"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:96
#: 94b5d1f342aa4893876afc31ec17af71
msgid ""
"**Local Tools:** - Tool not found: Check registration and imports - "
"Parameter errors: Verify JSON schema - Execution failures: Check BaseTool "
"inheritance - Import errors: Verify module structure"
msgstr ""
"**本地工具：**  \n"
"- 工具未找到：检查注册和导入  \n"
"- 参数错误：验证 JSON 模式  \n"
"- 执行失败：检查 BaseTool 继承  \n"
"- 导入错误：验证模块结构"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:102
#: a391612cbb1a47a08088a8a80c5b0c92
msgid ""
"**Remote Tools:** - Connection errors: Check server URL and network - "
"Authentication failures: Verify credentials - Timeout issues: Check server "
"performance - Discovery problems: Verify MCP server status"
msgstr ""
"**远程工具：**  \n"
"- 连接错误：检查服务器URL和网络  \n"
"- 身份验证失败：验证凭据  \n"
"- 超时问题：检查服务器性能  \n"
"- 发现问题：验证MCP服务器状态"

#: ../../expand_tooluniverse/reference/index.rst:108
#: 9c95d334d5c34284a127871c37e497e2
msgid ""
"**General:** - Configuration errors: Check JSON syntax - Permission issues: "
"Verify file access - Version conflicts: Check dependencies - Performance "
"issues: Profile and optimize"
msgstr ""
"**常规：**  \n"
"- 配置错误：检查 JSON 语法  \n"
"- 权限问题：验证文件访问权限  \n"
"- 版本冲突：检查依赖项  \n"
"- 性能问题：分析并优化"

